      <title>自2008年以来，亚洲股票大多数都在全球衰退的担忧中大多数</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/asian-stock-benchmarks-drops-most-in-14-years-on-tariff-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自2008年金融危机以来，亚洲的股票下跌，其主要基准滑倒，这是对贸易战对全球经济影响的担忧的广泛而深刻的抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/asian-stock-benchmarks-drops-most-in-14-years-on-tariff-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 02:53:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
